explanations.content:
Thay $z=a+bi$ vào biểu thức $\dfrac{z^2+z+1}{z^2-z+1}$ suy ra $a^2+b^2=1.$ $\\$
Tính $M=\dfrac{1-a^4-b^4}{1-a^6-b^6}=\dfrac{1-\left(a^4+b^4\right)}{1-\left(a^6+b^6\right)} 
=\dfrac{1-\left[(a^2+b^2)^2-2a^2b^2\right]}{1-\left[(a^2+b^2)^3-3a^2b^2(a^2+b^2)\right]}
=\dfrac{2}{3}.$
